To create a no-KYC digital product store, you'll need to choose a payment processor, such as NOWPayments, and integrate it with your website or online platform. You'll also need to set up a blockchain-based platform to secure your transactions and ensure the integrity of your digital products. Finally, you'll need to configure your digital product delivery system to automatically deliver products to buyers' wallets. With Web3 Wallet Connect ($19.99), you can easily integrate a frontend wallet with multi-chain QR generation and live price feeds, allowing buyers to pay in BTC, ETH, USDT, SOL, and 300 more coins."
